Hi,

We were recently informed that you had just completed a session with =
one of our
signers that their was not properly notarized. Please reach out =
to the signer
via email and offer a new session to properly complete the =
signing.

If this is not possible, you risk being suspended from the Open =
Call program
until further notice. When creating a new session we advise =
that you also use
the Invoice on Your Own Feature to offer the client a =
free session to cover the
charges since your payment is already being =
processed. We reserve the right to
reverse payment if this matter isn't =
addressed soon. Let us know if you have any
further questions or concerns.

Thank you!
